OL,5, A man's indefinite sentence for a      
OL,6, mobile phone theft has left him with   
OL,7, severe mental health problems after 12 
OL,8, years in prison, his sister said.      
OL,10,FThomas White was handed an imprisonment
OL,11,Ffor public protection (IPP) sentence   
OL,12,Fwith a minimum two-year tariff in 2012.
OL,14,FHe must complete rehabilitation before 
OL,15,Fbeing released, but Clara White said he
OL,16,Fhas not been able to access a scheme in
OL,17,Fany of the 16 prisons he has been in.  
OL,19,FShe said he had faced a "serious       
OL,20,Finjustice scandal".                    
